text: innu, samud janangadedege, (dutaragi) avara sahodara salih bandaru. Avaru helidaru; nanna janangadavare, allahanannu matra aradhisiri, nimage avana horatu bere yaru devarilla. Avane nim'mannu bhumiyinda srstisidanu mattu adaralli nim'mannu nelesidanu. Nivu avanalli ksameyannu bediri mattu avaneduru pascattapa padiri. Khanditavagiyu nanna odeyanu tumba nikatanu spandisuvavanu agiddane
